{"tid":259640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被螃蟹誤當生蠔　女沙灘裸曬陰部被夾傷","createTime":"2017-05-27T06:06:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T12:24:15.000Z","uid":7232,"like":69,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1386f2cb4a954c8df0008b304b03d592868ed15a","tid":259640,"uid":7232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T06:06:02.000Z","msg":"新加坡一名28歲女子，在樟宜海灘做裸體日光浴時，下體被一隻螃蟹夾傷。專家認為，螃蟹可能誤以為女子下體是生蠔而施襲。<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞《中國報》報導，女子日前與2名女友人到沙灘曬太陽，趁四下無人時，她們把衣服脫光，盡情享受日光浴。曬了15分鐘後，女子突然感到下體劇痛，起身一看，驚見一隻大螃蟹用大螯夾著她下體不放，不禁大叫。她的朋友見狀，上前協助把螃蟹移開。因為擔心蟹螯有毒，友人還為女子「吸毒液」、清潔傷口，並聯絡醫護人員到場。<br />\n<br />\n女子傷勢沒有大礙，傷口很快復原，疤痕也不明顯，但心理創傷可能需要點時間才能平復。新加坡法例禁止在沙灘上裸體，醫護人員也勸傷者，以後不要再裸曬。<br />\n<br />\n當地海洋生物學家說，螃蟹攻擊女性私處，是因為誤以為那是生蠔。他又說，蟹螯一般無毒，但若被夾地方很敏感，可能出現過敏反應。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170527/1127404/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170527%2F1127404%2F&d=1fGj8INSxoTFNm2qpumDFMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=9c3ceb68\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170527/1127404/</a>"},{"pid":"0be1bae93e7262d9dc15617edee0a000af25de09","tid":259640,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T06:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5237ae85b2dd9322de40b75dea76eff15d6e9d","tid":259640,"uid":21696,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T06:08:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">友人還為女子「吸毒液」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c27ed755c5823e68a8090ac7c5123ff01a430700","tid":259640,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T06:08:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f